title: TTG Asia takes a break to celebrate Singapore's birthday
text:
TTG Asia takes a break to celebrate Singapore's birthday Singapore, August 6, 2015 
Credit: Facebook / NDPeeps 

TTG Asia e-Daily will be taking a break for the public holidays on Friday, August 7 and Monday, August 10. 

News will resume on Tuesday, August 11. 

Happy National Day in advance to all Singaporean readers!
